      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been preserved with obsessive care. The exterior features original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating and entirely free of rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats still retain their factory matte finish and 'new car' scent, with no evidence of wear on the bolsters or carpets. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been housed in a climate-controlled environment and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships on a strict time-based schedule. It comes complete with all original manuals, two sets of keys, the original window sticker, and a comprehensive binder of service receipts. This is a pristine example of automotive excellence ready for a collection or a discerning owner who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
